line_1: The nymph between two chariot glasses,
line_2: While Cynthio ogles as she passes

line_1: Breaks Watch-men's Heads, and Chair-men's Glasses;
line_2: And thence proceeds to nicking Sashes:

line_1: The gentlemen fill'd up the sparkling glasses,
line_2: To drink to their King, to their country and lasses;

line_1: Repeats you Verses wrote on Glasses;
line_2: Five deep, He toasts the tow'ring Lasses;
